  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_sexual_assault_referral_centre">Sexual Assault Referral Centre</xref>
 is a 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_justice_organisation">Justice Organisation</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_sexual_assault_referral_centre">Sexual Assault Referral Centre</xref>
 (
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_sexual_assault_referral_centre">SARC</xref>
) is a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_location">LOCATION</xref>
 where people go for medical assessment and medical and forensic services following a sexual assault.  </p>
  <p>
For further information on Health and Justice healthcare, see the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
 website at: 
    <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/commissioning/health-just/"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Health and Justice</xref>
.  </p>

